Package pt.uc.dei.dtos

Class CourseUpdateDTO

java.lang.Object
pt.uc.dei.dtos.CourseUpdateDTO
public class CourseUpdateDTO extends Object
Data Transfer Object (DTO) for updating a course. All fields are optional; only provided fields will be updated.
